ActNational Capital Act
SubjectOrder Approving that the NCC Extend the Lease with Croisières de l'Outaouais Inc.
PrecisOrder approving that the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION grant two options to extend the lease with CROISIÈRES DE L’OUTAOUAIS INC., for a period of 30 years, beginning on April 1, 2027, for the real property located at the Jacques Cartier wharf facilities, or any comparable location in the vicinity of the Jacques Cartier wharf facilities, in Gatineau, Quebec.
AttachmentsAttachment
